有講, 點解香港無黎聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔還得起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n應該還俾承認的一個政權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=ca851295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=67a599f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&h=a10eff3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cf685836eb6c6541d31c3935fbf4bcbe65c379a","tid":1534901,"uid":144323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:09:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n課都無人罷丫<br />\n<br />\n今日 hku mtr station 照排長龍<br />\n<br />\n香港人可唔可以掙氣d"},{"pid":"323c635e172e19aefcfc02c9e184d910ff14d937","tid":1534901,"uid":226126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5161b483c9a736fcd645faca26a2514cb8417a23","tid":1534901,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:16:06.000Z","msg":"就算強姦係真<br />\n就算太子有人死<br />\n就算有人中真槍<br />\n<br />\n都咪撚再期望佢地會罷工跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e1262a4eb4565994fbc32eb7f993146c650ac3","tid":1534901,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s